quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,<Hai ureueng mukmin bek lale gata Deungon areuta napsu le leupah > Beu le ngon aneuk lale treuk ngon nyan Jeut gata dum han taingat Allah Soe-soe nyang pubuet teuma lagee nyan Bandum ureueng nyan rugoe that leupah
  63,10,Raseuki nyang Kamoe bri keu gata Tameubeulanja zakeuet seudeukah F Yoh goh troh mawot keunan bak gata 5 Watee nyan gata meunyesai teulah Watee nyan takheun Tuhanku pakon Han Neupeutrep lon bek mate bagah Neubri bacut treuk keu lon nyoe watee Mangat jeuet teuntee lon bri seudeukah Amai nyang saleh lon pubuet teuma
  63,11,Di Tuhan teuma han roe Neuubah s Barangri nyawong han Neubri tanggoh Meu ajai ka troh ka abeh sudah Tuhan that maklum peue nyang tapubuet Hana meubacut pih na meuilah